{"type": "article", "id": 24668, "title": "极简浴室家具组", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-30T07:00:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122130iaRCSB4KnI1Ufyph.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">丹麦设计工作室 Norm architects 在一年前推出了一个浴室系列，这是它的另一个系列，都在极简北欧风格中体现出优雅。无论是沙发、洗手池柜子还是墙上的架子都使用了纤细而方正的黑色金属做结构，搭配黑色的木材、皮垫或白色桌面，能看到包豪斯风格。在结构转折的细节处使用了黄铜来提亮，很古典。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122127IUPru8XiET3YNZFy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74816626\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122128m2bMwLxusZzKINl3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 235px; width: 375px; left: 514px; top: 1049px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122128t6pMgjoYHSahnVQC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122129zymg7Wkr5L8CPxiM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.36185819\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}